          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="glass-panel rounded-3xl p-8">
        <div class="space-y-6 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
          <div>
            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500">Statistiche 2025</p>
            <div class="mt-3 flex items-baseline gap-2 text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
              100%
              <span class="text-sm font-normal text-gray-500">clienti riconferma partnership</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
            <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white/70 p-4 shadow-sm dark:bg-black/40">
              <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500">AI Ready</p>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Contenuti ottimizzati per risposte su ChatGPT, Gemini e motori di ricerca generativi.</p>
