            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-primary">‚úì</span> <span class="font-semibold">Supporto prioritario WhatsApp</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-primary">‚úì</span> Piccole modifiche mensili incluse
            </li>
          </ul>
        </article>

        <article class="rounded-3xl border border-gray-200/60 bg-white/80 p-6 shadow-sm dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-black/40">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Landing page & Funnel</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">A partire da</p>
          <p class="text-3xl font-semibold text-primary">‚Ç¨300</p>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Perfetta per campagne mirate e lead generation geolocalizzata. Include copy ottimizzato per campagne AI e Google Ads.</p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500">Setup rapido</p>
        </article>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8 rounded-3xl border border-primary/20 bg-primary/10 p-6 text-center text-sm text-primary dark:border-primary/30 dark:bg-primary/20">
        Realizziamo anche <strong>Tessere NFC</strong> (da ‚Ç¨20), E-commerce complessi e integrazioni gestionali. Parliamone in consulenza.
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="clienti" class="py-20 bg-gray-50/70 dark:bg-white/5">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 text-center md:text-left md:flex-row md:items-end md:justify-between">
        <div>
